HEADWORD: Explodent
<hw>Ex*plod"ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An
instrument or agent causing explosion; an exploder; also, an
explosive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>See <er>Explosive</er>, <pos>n.</pos>, 2.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

